name: MARSWAP FARM
description: MSWAPF (MSWAP farm token). This token is designed to farm LP for Marswap exchange and projects that launch through us. In addition this will increase our volume and presence on the shibarium network as a DEX. It forms part of the ecosystem if MARSWAP and enables MSWAP farming as part of its utility. Following the success of MSWAP eth token the next phase of the project has been rolled out on the Shibarium Network
